headline: BofA Reinstates Fair Isaac (FICO) Coverage With Buy Rating, $1,900 PT Citing Strong Pricing Power
summary: Fair Isaac Corporation (NYSE:FICO) is one of the best growth stocks to buy for the next 20 years.
